Attempt to locate and load a dynamic library specified by a "libraryName" parameter

Parameters:
libraryName - The "libraryName" could be a library name or a full file name (but not a path)
paths - The "paths" parameter is optional and specifies paths where to look, and it will also search sub-directories
Throws:
WWRuntimeException - if attempt to load filed
IllegalArgumentException - if the libraryName parameter is null or empty
